xy*dy/dx + 3y^2 -x^2 = 0,  x>0
y' + 3y/x - x/y = 0
x^2
u = \frac{y}{x}
 xy\frac{\mathrm{d}y}{\mathrm{d}x} + 3y^2 -x^2 = 0 \\ 
 \frac{y}{x}\frac{\mathrm{d}y}{\mathrm{d}x} + 3\left(\frac{y}{x}\right)^2-1 = 0 \\ \text{Take $u = \frac{y}{x}$} \\ u\left(u + x\frac{\mathrm{d}u}{\mathrm{d}x}\right) + 3u^2-1 = 0 \\ ux\frac{\mathrm{d}u}{\mathrm{d}x} + 4u^2-1 = 0 \\ ux\frac{\mathrm{d}u}{\mathrm{d}x} = 1-4u^2 \\ \frac{u}{1-4u^2}\mathrm{d}u = \frac{\mathrm{d}x}{x} \\ 
